      <!--Use archref, not extref, to link to related collections.--><separatedmaterial encodinganalog="544 0">
         <head>Separated Material</head>
         <p>A copy of <emph render="italic">Las Tallas de Coro de Enrique Monjo en la Basilica de Tarrasa</emph> (Choir Statues of Enrique Monjo in the Basilica of Tarrasa), by Luis Monreal y Tejada, has been transferred to Rare Books for cataloging.  Please refer to &summitref; to locate this item.</p>
